Breaking the chains.

3 Complete Messages:

Your Time Is Coming
God Will Complete Your Incompletions
Make The Most Of Every Opprotunity
was very inspirational.  Want to get more.
Love this series of teaching..........!
Joel always has such a wonderful message for you. This is just another way of giving you the inspiration one needs in this day in time.
Love all of Mr. Joel Osteen books there are so many different things and feelings that some way you have been through or just thinking about he seems to be able to understand you
30 mins on Sunday just wasn't enough so now I have backup. He is infectious with his love of life and people.

I am a devote follower of Joel Osteen.  I think he is a gifted Minister.  I not only thought the value was an Excellent Value on this product, but you literally get 3 sermons on the purchase of this DVD!!  That's amazing!!

Joel Osteen is both Inspirational and Motivating and he brings the word of God into the mainstream so that everyone walks away understanding the word of God and can apply HIS word into their everyday life.  Thank you, Amazon for offering Joel Osteen or other inspirational messages from other ministers.

I recommend this purchase for anyone looking to be lifted up!!

Valarey
I was expecting a CD to listen to in the car but as it turned out to be a DVD I was pleasingly surprised. Joel & Victoria Osteen deliver timely messages from God.
Do not get this CD.  BORING! Not inspiring like I read.  Waste of money.  Would not purchase anything from Joel Osteen again.
It is very good for us to promote and encorage each other with good quality. Shipment is fast enough for us view and listen on the holidy travel.
A powerful and faith inspiring message can be found throughout this dvd. This man was born to teach about God and the religious sect.
